  "name": "RPlog_A_member_of_the_Rebel_Alliance_and_a_Traitor",
  "title": "A Member of the Rebel Alliance and a Traitor",
  "summary": "Captured and held in brutal sensory-deprivation conditions, New Republic Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard is dragged from her cell, subjected to a staged mock execution, and hauled before a bored, greasy Imperial Security Bureau interrogator. Wounded, parched, and starving, she spars defiantly with the officer, who methodically extracts her name and occupation while a stormtrooper batters her injured knees at his every nod. He insists she is not a diplomat but a spy and terrorist who corrupted the neutral Caspian government into arming the Rebellion, while Ambrosia furiously maintains she dealt only in truths and that the Caspian weapons trade was the free business of independent companies. When she finally yields her name in hope of water, the agent pours the pitcher onto the floor, then drinks the single glass himself before ordering her returned to her cell -- leaving the embittered ambassador to sigh that they have, at least, reached a common understanding.",
